<!--F8EF9C81CADB47138D0D6839F6A6AC8A-->  <HELP><![CDATA[There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reporting. There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: 
